    JoinCommand
    Joins the list of channels received.
    ModeCommand  
    NamesCommand
    Lists all nicknames that are visible to him.
    NickCommand
    Is used to give user a nickname or change the existing one.
    NoticeCommand
    This command sends a notice, that works similar to a private message.
    OperCommand
    A normal user uses the OPER command to obtain operator privileges.
    PartCommand
    Leaves the list of channels received, and if a message is set with that message.
    PassCommand
    Sets the password for the nickname when connecting.
    PingCommand
    This command represents a PING command sent by the server.
    PongCommand
    This command represents a PONG command (The response to a PING command).
    PrivmsgCommand
    Is used to send a message to a msgtarget.
    ReplyCommand  
    UserCommand
    This command must be used to register with the given username and realname.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    InvalidCommandException
    This exception is thrown when an invalid command created (Most probably when reading a command, or trying to send one).
